<:role: ROM Distilled — Lethe R1-R4 評価フレームワーク — ρ を超えて {#sec_01_framework} :>

<:data search_index:
  keywords: Lethe, CCL, evaluation_metrics, forgetful_functor, R1, R2, R3, R4, LQS, invariance, sensitivity, isomorphism, rho, code_similarity, Spearman
